resources.string: Welcome to Drinks and Dreams, your number one source for quick drinks at your favorite restaurant. We are a family driven business with core values. We are dedicated to giving you the very best of service, with a focus on quality, speed and security Founded in 2021 by Rasmus, Drinks and Dreams has come a long way from its beginnings in a a small basement in Aarhus. When Rasmus first started out, his passion for a more efficient restaurant service drove him to quit his day job, and gave him the impetus to turn hard work and inspiration into to a booming online store. We now serve customers all over world, and are thrilled to be a part of the efficient wing of the app industry.
